properties.Name: TransunionEmploymentRecord
properties.Description: The Employment Credit Report provided TransUnion only includes the latest employer.

Columns.Name: TransunionEmploymentRecordNumber
Columns.Description: The TransUnion Employment Record Number uniquely identifies an employment record within a TransUnion Credit Report.

Columns.Name: PositionStartDate
Columns.Description: The start date of the employment position.

Columns.Name: PositionEndDate
Columns.Description: The end date of the employment position.

Columns.Name: DateHired
Columns.Description: The date of employment with the employer.

Columns.Name: EmployerAddress
Columns.Description: The 'street/po box'' component of the employer address.

Columns.Name: EmployeeCity
Columns.Description: The 'city' component of the employer address.

Columns.Name: EmployeeState
Columns.Description: The 'state' component of the employer address.

Columns.Name: EmployerZipCode
Columns.Description: The 'zip code'' component of the employer address.

Columns.Name: IncomeAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of income associated with the employment.

Columns.Name: InFileSinceDate
Columns.Description: The date that the employment information has been in file.

Columns.Name: EffectiveDate
Columns.Description: The effective date of the employment information.

Columns.Name: TransunionEmploymentPositionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a TransUnion Employment
